" href=\"/favicon-16x16.png\" sizes=\"16x16\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"\n          geist_9e050971-module__05dp7a__className\n          bg-[#F7F6F3]\n          text-neutral-900\n          antialiased\n        \"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><header class=\"   sticky   top-0   z-50   border-b   border-neutral-200/60   bg-[#F7F6F3]/90   backdrop-blur-md   \"><div class=\"   mx-auto   flex   max-w-[1280px]   items-center   justify-between   px-6   py-5   \"><a class=\"   text-xl   font-light   tracking-[0.25em]   uppercase   text-neutral-900   \" href=\"/\">tinysorted</a><nav class=\"   hidden   md:flex   items-center   gap-8   text-sm   text-neutral-600   \"><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/minimalist-living\">Minimalist Living</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/storage-ideas\">Storage Ideas</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/kitchen\">kitchen</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/small-spaces\">Small Spaces</a></nav><a aria-label=\"Search\" class=\"   flex   items-center   justify-center   w-10   h-10   rounded-full   border   border-neutral-200   hover:bg-white   transition   \" href=\"/search\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></a></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><!--$--><main class=\"bg-[#F7F6F3] min-h-screen\"><section class=\"   max-w-[1100px]   mx-auto   px-6   \"><header class=\"   pt-24   pb-20   \"><p class=\"   uppercase   tracking-[0.25em]   text-xs   text-neutral-500   mb-5   \">Legal</p><h1 class=\"   text-5xl   md:text-7xl   font-light   tracking-[-0.04em]   leading-none   \">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"   mt-8   max-w-3xl   text-xl   leading-9   text-neutral-600   \">Your privacy matters to us. This page explains what information we collect and how we use it.</p></header><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Introduction</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted (&quot;we&quot;, &quot;our&quot;, or &quot;us&quot;) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, and protected whenever you visit our website.</p><p>By using this website, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Information We Collect</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>We may collect information that you voluntarily provide, including:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 mt-6\"><li>Name</li><li>Email address</li><li>Messages submitted through contact forms</li></ul><p class=\"mt-8\">We also automatically collect anonymous technical information including:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 mt-6\"><li>Browser type</li><li>Device information</li><li>IP address</li><li>Pages visited</li><li>Time spent on pages</li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Cookies</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted uses cookies to improve website performance, remember preferences, and analyze visitor behavior.</p><p>You may disable cookies in your browser settings, although some features of the website may no longer function properly.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Analytics</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>We may use services such as Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website. These services may collect anonymous usage data through cookies.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Advertising</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted may display advertisements through advertising partners such as Google AdSense.</p><p>These partners may use cookies to serve personalized ads based on your previous visits to this and other websites.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Affiliate Links</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Some articles may contain affiliate links.</p><p>If you purchase products through these links, TinySorted may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you.</p><p>Affiliate partnerships never influence our editorial opinions or recommendations.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Third-Party Services</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Our website may link to third-party websites including retailers, social media platforms, and external services.</p><p>We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those websites.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Your Rights</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 mt-6 space-y-3\"><li>Request access to your data</li><li>Correct inaccurate information</li><li>Delete your personal data</li><li>Withdraw consent</li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Data Security</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Children&#x27;s Privacy</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Changes to This Policy</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Contact</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p><p class=\"mt-6 font-medium\">hello@tinysorted.com</p></div></section></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"   mt-40   border-t   border-neutral-200   bg-[#F7F6F3]   \"><div class=\"   mx-auto   max-w-[1280px]   px-6   py-24   \"><div class=\"   grid   gap-16      md:grid-cols-2   lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]   \"><div><a href=\"/\"><h2 class=\"   text-2xl   font-light   uppercase   tracking-[0.32em]   text-neutral-900   transition   hover:opacity-70   \">Tinysorted</h2></a><p class=\"   mt-6   max-w-xl   text-neutral-600   leading-8   \">TinySorted helps people organize small spaces, simplify everyday living, and discover practical home solutions through thoughtfully researched articles and carefully selected product recommendations.</p><p class=\"   mt-6   text-sm   text-neutral-500   \">Practical ideas for better living.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Explore</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/decluttering\">Decluttering</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/small-spaces\">Small Spaces</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/storage-ideas\">Storage Ideas</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/kitchen\">Kitchen</a></nav></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Company</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/write-for-us\">Write For Us</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/advertise\">Advertise</a></nav></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Legal</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/affiliate-disclosure\">Affiliate Disclosure</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/disclaimer\">Disclaimer</a></nav></div></div><div class=\"   mt-20   border-t   border-neutral-200   pt-10   \"><p class=\"   max-w-4xl   text-sm   leading-7   text-neutral-500   \">TinySorted participates in various affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on this site, at no additional cost to you. Our recommendations are based on independent research and editorial judgment.</p></div><div class=\"   mt-12   flex   flex-col   gap-4      border-t   border-neutral-200   pt-8      md:flex-row   md:items-center   md:justify-between   \"><p class=\"   text-sm   text-neutral-500   \">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> TinySorted. All rights reserved.</p><div class=\"   flex   flex-wrap   gap-6      text-sm   text-neutral-500   \"><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/sitemap.xml\">Sitemap</a><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/rss.xml\">RSS</a><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/contact\">Support</a></div></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14rn1owgzaaej.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"LoadingBoundaryProvider\\\"]\\n2:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n3:I[79520,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[8821,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2tl5ylga63cnz.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n7:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n15:I[53348,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1-l_2hzb54z0b.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1x4-ievqljcrj.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.0wgildi0cnwt9.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><scr